version_description:
・ Bug fix
・ Addition of localization
・ Add skin instructions

・ Bug fix
・ Addition of localization
・ Add skin instructions

- Added support for "osu!taiko" score (.osz).
-The judgment position can be adjusted.
-Minor bug fixes.

-The speed can be finely adjusted.
-I put a big note in the setting so that even a single tap gives a high score.
-Fixed a gradual shift in long songs.
-The GOGO TIME processing was not working well in the place where there were no notes or bar lines, so I made it possible to use the modified one in the settings.
(If there is no problem, use the new process in the next version or later)
-The sound of the game in the advertisement is turned off.
-Minor bug fixes.
-Fixed a crash if there was a "." at the end of the file name.

-Fixed the behavior when the gauge is MAX.
-Added extended instruction so that the character spacing of FONT_S can be changed.
-Other bug fixes.

ver 1.3.0
-Fixed crashing at startup

ver 1.2.9
-Fixed the behavior when the gauge is MAX.
-Added extended instruction so that the character spacing of FONT_S can be changed.
-Other bug fixes.
